{
 "name": "RPlog_Return_of_the_Prodigal_Son",
 "title": "Return of the Prodigal Son",
 "summary": "In a hospital room, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios finds Paul Nighman being treated for a serious neck wound by a chiding medical droid, and confronts him sharply for failing to come in immediately -- leaving her and Luke worried sick. Paul, masking his pain and pride, claims he wasn't 'stable enough' to come at first, deflecting her cool, simmering anger. As the droid clears his infection and tends his injury, the two navigate the tension, hurt, and unspoken feelings between them, with Shenner, the General Skeezix Calhoun, and Gabrielle in the wings. The prodigal's return becomes a charged reckoning over trust and worry.",
